Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.05,0:00:09.00,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord1\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.01,0:00:18.61,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.88,0:00:28.58,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:33.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:38.65,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:51.26,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, singing those chords of happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:01:00.96,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:05.80,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:11.47,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:20.77,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:33.27,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:49.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, my little ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:52.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby to advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:52.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:53.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Advancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are our reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.78,0:02:01.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Left, forty degrees! Main armament, standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:06.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance, 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:09.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Load shell. Incendiary round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:09.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:12.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Olga!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:13.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:17.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been canned in this thing for three days! I'm not dying until I get a shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:19.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Target locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:20.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:30.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna, signal the forces to our rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:35.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have destroyed enemy unit. Take up our rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:36.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:38.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia, cover her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:40.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Y- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:46.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's flashing out there, but there's no thunder. Just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Three o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:49.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:57.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Bamboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:29.49,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}Chirping Crickets - Floating Lights on the River
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:33.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:36.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't get clean if you don't scrub harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:06.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This building gets way too cold in the winter, but thank God it's cool in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.85,0:05:10.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Weren't Filicia and Rio in charge of the laundry today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:13.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They said they were busy so they asked us to do it for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:14.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:16.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:20.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wasn't hungry, so we could have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this one's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Are you starting on dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:33.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch. What are you making? You shouldn't play with your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:36.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for {\i1}Obon{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's this {\i1}Obon{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:43.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fiesta des Lumières{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:44.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:49.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fiesta des Lumières{\i0} is an event specific to the southern part of Helvetia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It originated in a local belief that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:56.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,for a short period during the summer, the souls of the dead would return to the world of the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:06:00.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper lanterns are floated down the river as a symbol of their return to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:05.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In some regions, the festival is called {\i1}Obon{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:08.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So it's the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Souls returning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:21.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait! What does that mean? Does that mean ghosts come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In one sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:26.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper lanterns? That sounds so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We used to hold bonfires back in my village, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:33.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Dead people go to Heaven and stay there forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:35.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the evil spirits wander around on earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Church...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Mind lending us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:48.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you two go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, aren't those...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They looked delicious, so we bought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:53.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And these too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Father. I told you, it's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:13.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom and dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:17.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you did a really good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:21.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Even the Church approves of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That Fi-whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:27.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The central diocese would start a riot,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:28.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not much of a reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:38.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In my village, we would make horses and cows out of cucumbers and eggplants for our ancestors to ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:46.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And to console our ancestors, we would all dance together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:50.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two making them too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:53.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Last year we only watched, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:10.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maintaining smooth cultural relations with the local residents is also part of our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get into details, it's just another festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:25.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:30.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1}Sound of the Skies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:32.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:42.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:44.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just made a little mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:50.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's pretty rare for you to make a mistake like that, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're not Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:57.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's been pretty hot these last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't slept very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get a little rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:10.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:14.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Commander's acting a bit weird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:19.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't eat her lunch, and then she buys watermelons without checking our food budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:22.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure even she has her reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:27.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll talk to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:28.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has a part of themselves they don't want anyone to know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:41.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what happened, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I read the files.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:46.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was there when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:47.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:12.85,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your elbow into it. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:17.13,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:24.36,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,And then a ghost that looked just like the Commander
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:33.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There used to be millions of things living in this ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone ever tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:42.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They say the world is slowly dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:46.17,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and eventually, all humanity will fall completely into ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:48.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,people talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:53.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it were true,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:57.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,then what are we fighting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:14.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideographs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:02.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could read your final words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:10.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be a soldier from-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Olga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Marlina...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:30.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:32.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:34.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:38.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:49.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So there are still people alive in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:51.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:13:59.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:01.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:03.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:09.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:13.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.66,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:39.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You are just the dregs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:46.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The last few bubbles in the bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:54.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The world will never shine as it did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:57.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't decide that for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:14:59.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So just end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:12.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Living pathos in the dregs of the world, in this despair? It's far too desolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:15.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:20.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Does remaining in this world have any meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:22.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:47.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:57.72,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I am here! I am alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:22.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:31.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If only my corps had arrived half a day sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,it wouldn't have turned out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, Princess Iria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:47.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:52.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You completely ignored the {\i1}Fiesta des Lumières{\i0} last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the change of faith?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:02.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a pretty color?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:05.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Treize is famous for these. I bought them at the flea market.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:11.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're amazing! They're so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.71,0:17:13.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:16.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She used to mean everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:25.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I wanted to protect my country, my people, like she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any meaning in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:39.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So if she really did come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted her to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:49.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They're worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:53.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I may have made them worry a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:55.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've failed as a Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:57.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't the only ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I'm... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:06.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter! Just don't try to shoulder it all yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:08.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can listen to what you have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:10.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:14.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take your offer and tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:21.84,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've put on some weight this summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:22.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:25.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't lose it, I might not fit into my winter uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:31.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that if you only eat watermelon for a while, you can lose weight, so I thought I would try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:33.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you stop playing dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:41.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the front lines at the battle at Vingt-et-Un and-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:46.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you thought I was remembering that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:49.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Y- You weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:56.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we head down too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:17.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So you made one too, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:20.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I believe in souls or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's part of my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:26.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you sending, Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My old friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and a soldier whose name I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:36.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who helped me realize the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:45.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about anything, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:48.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be able to help, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:50.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I made you worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:56.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:03.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to worry about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:07.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you always worry about me, Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:11.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I make you worry. I want to worry about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:15.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love you, Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:21.61,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you too, Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:25.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Always stay the way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:26.90,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:29.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always trying to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:35.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,not to fear putting my feelings into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:40.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.74,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:49.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:51.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you three...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:00.93,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:14.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Until next year then, ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:23.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad. Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.09,0:21:35.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:36.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:39.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:49.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rio, you were just asking if there were any meaning in this world, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.25,0:21:50.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.28,0:21:55.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I survived the battle alone, I've pondered the same question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:59.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I, alone, survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:03.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there any meaning in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:02.30,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. You can't just space out like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:04.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:09.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There can't possibly be any meaning in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:14.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that wonderful in its own right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:20.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if there isn't any, we can find our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.95,0:22:26.54,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And I found mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:29.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My meaning in being alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:33.52,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And so even the priest joined in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:34.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And then? And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:37.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he was really bad at it, so Sister Yumina...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:45.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them to suffer the way I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:47.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:58.03,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:01.50,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:19.26,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:25.35,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:34.13,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:38.73,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:40.36,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.45,0:23:44.70,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:45.91,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:51.75,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:49.34,0:23:51.75,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.93,0:23:57.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8\3c&HE5A9EA&}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:24:03.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:09.56,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:14.51,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.96,0:24:26.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(320,180)\c&H020202&\bord0}Next time: Telephone Duty - Declare a State of Emergency
